   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting" image="QN_Npc_Geraint.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting-a" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What? Why should I...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>I'm moving forward to build a statue of the <FONT color=#a82424>Gold Dragon</FONT> to enhance the loyalty of the people.<BR>As part of the team, I hope you will do your part responsibly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting-a" image="QN_Npc_Saint_BlackSmith_Dwarf.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting-b" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>So I asked <FONT color=#a82424>Blacksmith Berlin</FONT> what the cost would be, but I haven't heard back from him.<BR>How about you go to him and find out what the cost will be?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-accepting-acceppted" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Busy Blacksmith$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-1" image="QN_Npc_Saint_BlackSmith_Dwarf.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>Find out how much of the statue has been done from <FONT color=#a82424>Blacksmith Berlin</FONT>.<BR>I thought making a statue would be an easy job....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1" image="QM_HoundNormal_2.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-a" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Berlin starts to complain)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Oh, I'm so busy! I'll be still busy if I had ten hands....<BR>It's like I can get a <FONT color=#a82424>hound</FONT> and make him work for me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-a" image="QN_Npc_Duke_Stwart.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-b" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He was asking when can it be done.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>What were you doing there? ...Um? Duke? Statue?<FONT color=#7e12d2> (Berlin picks his nose)</FONT><BR>Oh~ Statue! I thought the <FONT color=#a82424>Duke</FONT> went crazy after the war, but he was being serious...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-c" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Berlin looks through the log)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>When can it be done? Tell him I'll make him about after ten years later!<BR>...No. If I do that, the Duke will send some men and force me to make it....Well, let me see.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-d" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ok.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>There are lots of broken weapons because of the war. So it's my job to fix them first. We don't know when will the monsters attack us next so how can we protect <FONT color=#a82424>Saint Haven</FONT> with broken weapon? Isn't that right?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-e" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything I can help?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>We don't have any supplies to fix weapons but a statue? God, he doesn't know anything about this world.<BR>We don't even have enough forces to collect reusable weapons!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-2" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ok.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>What? It's good for me! I wanted to buy some hounds to pick up some material but I guess you could do better job. Please go and get me some <FONT color=#a82424>Piece of broken iron</FONT>!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-2" image="QW_33.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Defeat Pirate Swamp Lizardmen fro <FONT color=#a82424>Core of Lonely Island</FONT> and get their <FONT color=#a82424>Piece of broken iron</FONT>. You can get their spear head. Please get me 10 pieces.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-a" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Snatches the material)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Oh! You're back!<BR>Well, give me those <FONT color=#a82424>Piece of broken iron</FONT>!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-4" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ok.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>We are in such a bad situation so we even have to reuse the weapons of monsters.<BR>So go and tell this to <FONT color=#a82424>Duke Stuart</FONT>, I am so busy right now, I'm not in a condition to care about the statue.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Well see you again.<BR>I have lot of work to do. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Berlin continues to blow with the bellows.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-4-a" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm back. Forsaken Islet... (Explain what happened)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>What took you so long? I've just asked you to get a quotation of the statue.<BR>You look like you went to <FONT color=#a82424>Forsaken Islet</FONT> to see the <FONT color=#a82424>Blacksmith</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-4-a" image="QW_33.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-4-b" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Duke takes a big breath)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>Going all the way to the <FONT color=#a82424>Forsaken Islet Core</FONT>, you must have troubled yourself.<BR>Hmm. Well, that's how all the adventurers seem like.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-4-c" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Other way?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>Anyway, summing what you've said so far, we can't build the statue due to lack of iron scrap.<BR>Uhm... it's like I can force him to make it if we are short of material. I would have to find an other way.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n041_duke_stwart-4-d" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n041_duke_stwart-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Duke Stuart$<BR>I would have to find a way to get iron. Thanks for your work.<BR>I'll get in touch if I need you again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
